            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pie is in the oven, peel your <strong>potatoes</strong> and chop them into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 10-12 min or until fork-tender, then once done, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1643798328320-x200.jpg",
