            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>creamy salmon & leek pot pie</strong> with the <strong>lemony parsley mash </strong>and<strong> peas </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>lemon wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
